  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The creature has a bonus on initiative checks equal to its mythic ranks. As a free action on its turn, it can expend one use of <a class=\"entity-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; background-image: none; background-color: initial; padding: 0px; color: #ff6400; border: none;\" draggable=\"false\" data-pack=\"pf-content.pf-universal-monster-rules\" data-id=\"emNdW1Y7gFdGwNpo\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; text-decoration-line: underline;\">mythic power</span></a> to take an additional standard action during that turn. This additional standard action can&rsquo;t be used to cast a spell. It can&rsquo;t gain an extra action in this way more than once per round.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Format</em>: amazing initiative</p>\n<p><em>Location</em>: Special Attacks.</p>",
